</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-45_ pf-text-1"><strong>Call for help</strong> - Dial 999 immediately if you suspect a child is in shock. Early medical intervention is critical.



















</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-47_ pf-text-1"><strong>Positioning </strong>- Lay the child down with their legs raised slightly (unless injury prohibits this), which can help increase blood flow back to vital organs.




















